item.title: Connection problem
item.dc:creator: @wetodded wetodded
item.description:
@wetodded wrote:

This means that the client you are using does not support the items on the server. What you need to do is get a client that comes with a server, and if not, look for a server that is compatible with Client.silabsoft.org, or moparisthebest.com.
